      "message": "explicit \u003e\u003e implicit\n\nif a test result doesn\u0027t have `disabled_test:false` explicitly, then it is possible that test framework wasn\u0027t updated to emit this tag for disabled tests.\n\nbut I don\u0027t feel strongly about this. I was also a bit of a fence whether this should go into TestMetadata message as a first-class-citizen.",
